        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Militia organization.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>Robert Keykendall Captain of the Militia of the <placeName>Colorado 
district</placeName></persName> being about to remove from Said district, therefore by these
presents I do appoint <persName>James Ross</persName> <persName>Captain of the Militia</persName> of said
District to act as such untill the final organization of the <persName>Battalion</persName>
at which time a general election will be held for all the <persName>militia
officers of the <placeName>Colony</placeName></persName>,   the Subordinate officers and <persName>privats </persName>of said<pb n="716"/>
<placeName>Colorado district</placeName> are therefore commanded to recognize and obey
the said <persName>James Ross</persName> as their <persName>Captain </persName>under the pains and penalties
prescribed by law.</p>

<p>Enclosed I send you the Copy of a commission appointing <persName>James
Ross captain of the <placeName>Colorado district</placeName></persName>, you will therefore deliver
up the command of sd district to Said <persName>James Ross</persName> and also the public
powder in your possession</p>

<p><persName>Alexander Jackson</persName> will by public notice notify the <persName>Inhabitants</persName>
of the above district to convene at his house on the <date when="1823-12-15">15 instant</date>, for
the election ordered in the above.</p>

<p><placeName>St. Felipe de Austin</placeName></p>

<p><date when="1823-12-05">Dcr 5 1823&#8212;3d and 2d</date></p>

<p><persName>S. F. A.</persName></p>

<p><persName>L[ieutenant] C[olonel] M[ilitia]</persName></p>

        </div1>
